cture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/5jBqfgzHTLUEFswjvWrIjD?si=l337aEX1RY6O-t79dUNA7A&#038;context=spotify%3Aalbum%3A0JfaJAEBTdTVlfczvCZYdl&#038;nd=1&#038;dlsi=b365a52c671f42ce&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>琼斯还分享了艺术品，他说这是受法国裔艺术家路易丝·布尔乔瓦（Louise Bourgeois）的一幅画的启发。</p><p>他说：“我去了纽约，参观了一些画廊，看到&#39;艺术是保证了理智&#39;，这是路易丝·布尔乔瓦（Louise Bourgeois）的一幅画。”</p><p> “她认为艺术是一种精神康复的一种形式，也是处理困难情绪的一种方式。拼写首先吸引了我，然后刻在粉红色瓷砖上的单词的简单性。因此，我尝试刮擦自己的头衔，灵感来自三十年前的艺术学校老师。我喜欢它。我喜欢粉红色的简单性。粉红色专辑诞生了。” </p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://ecp.yusercontent.com/mail?url=https%3A%2F%2Flh7-qw.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXcQrhUh_mb3r5sXXVg2A5o8R2WdKaOeY9AgWatTnx-csOSXyOEgeXArN-ZvsjMA8D_j-EJ5uGQAHuc4e3lwPNT1TN6jy2urAxWlhpOd498pwKZLDdcgNhd7CbJDHkDdIjhe_eP2kh6fLeg4jFg3IHk%3Fkey%3DI2511Ei9W31RU6aCwwfG4yZj&amp;t=1738220357&amp;ymreqid=7d300e6f-2dd5-6f8f-1cd0-070001018100&amp;sig=z_4si6Kl7aeDnstleoO4EQ--~D" /></p><p>这是在琼斯（Jones） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-jones-reveals-when-to-expect-stereophonics-new-single-and-album-3825973">最近嘲笑了本月初的一张新专辑和单曲</a>之后。</p><p>乐队此前宣布在8月<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jake-bugg">16</a>日<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/stereophonics-tickets/artist/795944" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在</a>诺福克皇家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blossoms">桑德林汉姆</a>庄园举行的大型标题表演。</p><p>他们还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stereophonics-announce-2025-stadium-anthems-uk-and-ireland-tour-3800071">在6月和7月开始英国和爱尔兰的“体育场国歌”之旅</a>，最终在加的夫公国体育场的大型家乡演出中。请参阅<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stereophonics-announce-2025-stadium-anthems-uk-and-ireland-tour-3800071">此处</a>的完整列表，并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/stereophonics-tickets/artist/795944" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到门票。</p><p>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-sting-stereophonics-announced-headliners-isle-of-wight-festival-2025-3796064">还将</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克（Justin Timberlake）<