wants-to-be-in-a-band-3828351">说，他对成为独奏艺术家不感兴趣，因为他“只想加入乐队”</a> 。</p><p>他还透露，他和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Elton-John">埃尔顿·约翰爵士（Elton John）</a>的妈妈曾经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-says-he-once-left-an-elton-john-gig-with-sir-eltons-mum-because-they-didnt-know-any-songs-3829315">不了解他的任何歌曲，曾经离开了传奇的摇滚明星</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-admits-hes-never-eaten-pizza-or-curry-as-hes-allergic-to-several-items-3833089">林戈·斯塔尔（Ringo Starr）一生中从未吃过比萨饼或咖喱：“这让我立即生病”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
